OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1778137535
OL,3,CShoplifter who stole from charity shop
OL,4,Cjailed
OL,6,FA prolific shoplifter from Chichester,
OL,7,Fwho stole from premises including a
OL,8,Fcharity shop, has been jailed.
OL,10,FMwiya Kamutumwa, 25, of West Broyle,
OL,11,FChichester, admitted multiple thefts
OL,12,Fand breaches of a Criminal Behaviour
OL,13,FOrder.
OL,15,FThe 25-year-old, also known as Kush,
OL,16,Ftargeted stores including the British
OL,17,FHeart Foundation Shop, where he stole
OL,18,Fclothing and a backpack in October
OL,19,F2025.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
