PN,41702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1778137535
OL,3,CShoplifter who stole from charity shop
OL,4,Cjailed
OL,6,FKamutumwa admitted 17 shop thefts, 13
OL,7,Fbreaches of a Criminal Behaviour
OL,8,FOrder, burglary other than a dwelling,
OL,9,Fand obstructing a police officer in
OL,10,Fthe execution of their duty at
OL,11,FPortsmouth Court on 15 April 2026.
OL,13,FKamutumwa, of West Broyle, Chichester,
OL,14,Fwas sentenced to a total of four years
OL,15,Fin prison.
OL,17,FBetween February and March 2026,
OL,18,FKamutumwa committed 14 shop theft
OL,19,Foffences, and breached a Criminal
OL,20,FBehaviour Order nine times.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
