PN,41703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1778137535
OL,3,CShoplifter who stole from charity shop
OL,4,Cjailed
OL,6,FHe targeted the Co-op in East Street
OL,7,Fin Chichester three times, taking
OL,8,FProsecco, chocolate and washing
OL,9,Fdetergent.
OL,11,FKamutumwa also entered the One Stop
OL,12,Fstore in St Paul's Road on three
OL,13,Foccasions, taking milkshake, beer, and
OL,14,FProsecco.
OL,16,FHe admitted further thefts at Waitrose
OL,17,Fin Via Ravenna, Tk Maxx in East
OL,18,FStreet, and Marks and Spencer in
OL,19,FPortfield Retail Park.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
