FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1778137535
OL,3,CShoplifter who stole from charity shop
OL,4,Cjailed
OL,6,FSpeaking after the case, District
OL,7,FCommander Chief Inspector Adam McCaig
OL,8,Fsaid: "Kamutumwa is a prolific
OL,9,Foffender who has shown no regard for
OL,10,Fthe impact his offences have had on
OL,11,Fstaff and our communities.
OL,13,F"So I am pleased he is serving a
OL,14,Fcustodial sentence.
OL,16,F"We understand the impact retail crime
OL,17,Fcan have on businesses, staff and the
OL,18,Fwider community, and tackling
OL,19,Fshoplifting remains a priority for us.
OL,26,@pD@GOUuD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
