PN,41705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1778137535
OL,3,CShoplifter who stole from charity shop
OL,4,Cjailed
OL,6,F"While recent reporting does not
OL,7,Findicate a significant increase in
OL,8,Fshoplifting, we recognise that any
OL,9,Fincident can have a real impact and
OL,10,Fwill always be taken seriously.
OL,12,F"We continue to work alongside local
OL,13,Fretailers and partner agencies to
OL,14,Fsupport effective reporting and
OL,15,Fpromote crime prevention measures.
OL,26,@tD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
