PN,41706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1778137535
OL,3,CShoplifter who stole from charity shop
OL,4,Cjailed
OL,6,F"Visible policing and community
OL,7,Freassurance are central to our
OL,8,Fapproach, and through ongoing activity
OL,9,Fwe are focused on identifying and
OL,10,Fdealing with those responsible for
OL,11,Foffences, particularly repeat
OL,12,Foffenders.
OL,14,F"We are committed to supporting local
OL,15,Fbusinesses and will take action where
OL,16,Foffences are identified and evidence
OL,17,Fallows.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
